def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1, n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1, i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print(i+1)

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1, n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1, i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print(i+1)

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1, n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1, i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print(i+1)

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1, n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(i+1):
            print(j+1, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(1, i+2):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1, i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()

        print()

        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print(i+1)

def sequences(n):
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print(j, end=" ")
        print()
